00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,000
 To je to...

776
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,000
 I to je strašna kvaliteta.

777
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:15,000
 Jer imaš puno slučava i mojih kolega

778
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:18,000
