00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:06,000
 ako provali strana...

826
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:09,000
 Ja pucao protiv, četiri dana pre protiv Bilba,

827
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:12,000
 mi dobijemo 1:09, drugi minut, ja pucam, dam gol.

