863
00:38:57,000 --> 00:39:00,000
 Teren je najmanje bitan na kraju u neko vreme.

864
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:02,000
 I to troši malo, jel?

865
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:04,000
 I takako troši.

866
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:13,000
 Sad ovako, kad bih te pitao kojem klubu si se najbolje osjećao, za koji se najviše vezam, šta je to što ti prije prva padne na pamet?

867
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:14,000
 Koji je to klub?

868
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,000
 Partizan, jasno.

869
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:20,000
 To je meni san snova bio da igram za Maribor.

870
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:22,000
 Nažalost to nije.

871
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:25,000
 Onda za Partizan i da dam gol u derbiju.

872
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:29,000
 To je cela moja porodica Partizanovci.

873
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:35,000
 To su san snova i to mi se odmah, brzo mi se to nekako desilo.

874
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:39,000
 To je bilo...

875
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:45,000
 Znači, kad si mladi i kad imaš ono, tebi volio da igraš u Partizanu.

876
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:50,000
 Znači, ga ti ona dođe lopta i kaže: "Kome volio da imam zvezdne?" normalno.

877
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:56,000
 Interesantno i drago me čut, porod svih klubova kojima si nastupio da je to prva asocijacija.

878
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:59,000
 Neuspjeh, šta smatraš svojim najvećim neuspjehom?

879
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:03,000
 Je li to ovo finale i promrašanje danesteraciju?

880
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:10,000
 Teško bi, teško bi, teško bi rekao da je finale neuspjeh.

881
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:17,000
 Neuspjeh je jedino, to moram reći, onaj odlazak sa svetskog prvenstva.

882
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:19,000
 To je neuspjeh. Definitivno.

883
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:21,000
 To nikom ne bi poželeo.

884
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:24,000
 Niko nije bio spreman za to.

885
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:26,000
 Jednom se desile velike stvari.

886
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:36,000
 Mislim da je tad falio jedan, nekako, ljudsko razmjena mišljenja.

887
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:42,000
 Jer sportisti, ja nisam vidio sportista koji je loš čoveku i levo, desno.

888
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:44,000
 Sad pričam i o trenerima.

889
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:47,000
 Ali nije bilo, nije niko povezovan, neki nije da poveže to.

890
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:50,000
 Želost politika je uvijek, ali s druge strane...

891
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:53,000
 O tome da ne pričam, naočito u Sloveniji.

892
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:56,000
 Havimo na ovaj reprezentativni dio.

893
00:40:56,000 --> 00:41:00,000
 80 utaknice, ali tako?

894
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:01,000
 81, ja mislim.

895
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:03,000
 35 golova.

896
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:05,000
 Sa Slovenijom treba dati.

897
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:07,000
 Jer to si stalno iza.

898
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:10,000
 Stalno 50 metara od golo, 60 metara od golo.

899
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:12,000
 Da, jel misliš...

900
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:14,000
 A nisam bio center for.

901
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,000
 Znam.

902
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:16,000
 Nisam na špic.

903
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:17,000
 Znam.

904
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,000
 Znači ja sam tu neka lutelica.

905
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:20,000
 Ti si pretečao kao lažnih luteljuših.

906
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,000
 Da.

907
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,000
 Ja sam tu ove tu...

908
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,000
 Napadača.

909
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:25,000
 Malo, malo na intuiciju.

910
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:27,000
 Na intuiciju prostora.

911
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:29,000
 Ko šta može, ko šta ne može.

912
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:31,000
 Pa sam to iskoristavao.

913
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:32,000
 Šta je taj trenutak?

914
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,000
 Ko igrač može to?

915
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,000
 Ko će to?

916
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:36,000
 Znači ja sam bio puno razmišljavao

917
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:38,000
 na samom igralištu.

918
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,000
 To mi je dalo prednost.

919
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:42,000
 Jer sad, ti kad bi pogledao moje,

920
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:44,000
 ne znam, sposobnosti neke,

921
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:46,000
 da mi da neko na kompjuter fizičke,

922
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,000
 ako što sad rade,

923
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,000
 algoritme.

924
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:50,000
 Lila.

925
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:52,000
 Ali uvek sam se nad...

926
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:54,000
 Znači nemam to šta mogu da imam.

927
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:55,000
 Mogu da imam predviđanje.

928
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:56,000
 Mogu da razmišljam

929
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:58,000
 gde će lopta da padne,

930
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,000
 gde ne ima prostora.

931
00:41:59,000 --> 00:42:00,000
 Šta može sa igrač?

932
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:02,000
 Šta ne može sa igrač?

933
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,000
 Šta ne može sa igrač?

934
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:04,000
 To mi je šah pomogao to.

935
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:10,000
 Ali to je ljepota nogometar zapravo.

936
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:11,000
 Koliko god se mi je trudili,

937
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:13,000
 znanstveno i statistički,

938
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:15,000
 da stavimo na papir,

939
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:17,000
 ima jako puno prostora

940
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:19,000
 koje je teško objasniti.

941
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,000
 Pogotovo ta intuicija,

942
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,000
 pogotovo ta osjećaj,

943
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,000
 timing za prostor,

944
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:25,000
 za nekakvu anticipaciju.

945
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:26,000
 I to se ne može izračunati.

946
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:27,000
 Ne, ne.

947
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,000
 Mislim da mi je tu pomogao šah.

948
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:30,000
 i možda i moja životna priča,

949
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:32,000
 ideš u Belgrad Borise,

950
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:33,000
 igraš u Zrenim Borise,

951
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,000
 ideš u Petrenim Borise,

952
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,000
 da bi se izborio,

953
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:37,000
 nije samo nogometni kvalitet.

954
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:38,000
 Znači,

955
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:40,000
 to je skup nekih stvari.

956
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:41,000
 Razmišljanje,

957
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:42,000
 takmičarsko,

958
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:44,000
 šta trener priča,

959
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:46,000
 da vidim da nešto ne omanem,

960
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:48,000
 da mi ne može da mi kaže,

961
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,000
 ne igraš zbog ovog.

962
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:51,000
 onda ideš u Portugalu,

963
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:53,000
 dva stranca mogu da igraju.

964
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,000
 Da, da.

965
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:55,000
 A šesti u klubu.

966
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:56,000
 Šesti u klubu.

967
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:57,000
 A nisam ja došao,

968
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:59,000
 nisam ja španac.

969
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,000
 Ja sam Slovenija mali,

970
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,000
 ne znam gde je.

971
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:03,000
 Dva milionski.

972
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:04,000
 kako je kad tu,

973
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:07,000
 kad imaš ti,

974
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:08,000
 ne znam,

975
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:09,000
 menadžera koji je

976
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,000
 s naših prostora

977
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:11,000
 i njihov.

978
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:12,000
 Uvijek će njihov da igraju.

979
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,000
 Jer je njihov menadžer.

980
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:14,000
 Absolutno.

981
00:43:14,000 --> 00:43:15,000
 Ja dok se nisam u Portugalu,

982
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:16,000
 u Guimaraesu,

983
00:43:16,000 --> 00:43:17,000
 još toliko nije bilo,

984
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:18,000
 to već u Portu,

985
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:19,000
 u,

986
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:20,000
 ali sam imao sreće

987
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:21,000
 da sam imao vegu.

988
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:22,000
 Da.

989
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:23,000
 Ko zna kako bi ja prošao.

990
00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:24,000
 U Portu,

991
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:24,000
 znaš kako,

992
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:25,000
 puno interesa.

993
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:27,000
 Ja bih imel ispričati

994
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:28,000
 jednom priči,

995
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:29,000
 Fernando Santos,

996
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,000
 bio trener,

997
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,000
 ja ga volim,

998
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:35,000
 s Trile Madore,

999
00:43:35,000 --> 00:43:36,000
 nije već imao to iskustvo.

1000
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:38,000
 Porto je već bila formirana ekipa,

1001
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:39,000
 imamo tamo

1002
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:40,000
 mangupi,

1003
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:41,000
 igrači,

1004
00:43:41,000 --> 00:43:42,000
 stari,

1005
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:43,000
 i sad puno interesa.

1006
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:44,000
 Puno.

1007
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:46,000
 Znaš samo kako je nogovrat.

1008
00:43:46,000 --> 00:43:47,000
 I gledam jednom je za sobem

1009
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:48,000
 i kaže:

1010
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:49,000
 "Za, to će imamo malo."

1011
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:50,000
 Tamo poveći:

1012
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:51,000
 "Brazilci i Portovalci

1013
00:43:51,000 --> 00:43:52,000
 je stalno frka,

1014
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:53,000
 ja i Drula negdje između.

1015
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:54,000
 Nedirajte nas

1016
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:55,000
 i vi se svađate kog hoćete."

1017
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:56,000
 Kaže:

1018
00:43:56,000 --> 00:43:57,000
 "Pa vidi ovaj artu,

1019
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:59,000
 on već zna da će igrati sutra."

1020
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:03,000
 Šefe je puno interesa,

1021
00:44:03,000 --> 00:44:04,000
 polako,

1022
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:05,000
 nemoj da,

1023
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:06,000
 polako,

1024
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:07,000
 vidi malo,

1025
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:08,000
 vidjet ćeš,

1026
00:44:08,000 --> 00:44:09,000
 i onda normalno imaš te sastanke

1027
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:10,000
 ovaj od tamo.

1028
00:44:10,000 --> 00:44:12,000
 On zna da će igrati.

1029
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:13,000
 Ja još nizam neko sastanke.

1030
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:14,000
 A šta ćeš?

1031
00:44:14,000 --> 00:44:15,000
 Onda plivaš tu.

1032
00:44:15,000 --> 00:44:16,000
 Trener plivaš.

1033
00:44:16,000 --> 00:44:17,000
 Snalaziti, improvizirati.

1034
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:18,000
 Normalno.

1035
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:19,000
 I šta ti to znači?

1036
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:20,000
 Znači,

1037
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:22,000
 ko je jači menadžer,

1038
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:24,000
 s obzirom su kvalitete tu negdje.

1039
00:44:24,000 --> 00:44:25,000
 Tako je.

1040
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:26,000
 To ti je tako,

1041
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:27,000
 to je život.

1042
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:28,000
 ko je zapravo kao da je Švanka,

1043
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:30,000
 ako je utakmica Lila,

1044
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,000
 ako si odigrao prosječno,

1045
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:33,000
 prvo se upira prstom u stranca,

1046
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,000
 zašto oni do njoj razliku?

1047
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:35,000
 Da.

1048
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,000
 I nije se lako,

1049
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:37,000
 nije se lako izboriti,

1050
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:38,000
 onaj,

1051
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:40,000
 izgurat tu nekakvu karijeru inozemnu,

1052
00:44:40,000 --> 00:44:41,000
 napraviti,

1053
00:44:41,000 --> 00:44:44,000
 pogotovo iz nekakvih manjih sredina,

1054
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:46,000
 ali opet su nam omogućile,

1055
00:44:46,000 --> 00:44:48,000
 dali su nam njako dobre temelje.

1056
00:44:48,000 --> 00:44:50,000
 Znaš šta su oni volili kod nas?

1057
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:51,000
 Karakter.

1058
00:44:51,000 --> 00:44:52,000
 Da.

1059
00:44:52,000 --> 00:44:53,000
 Karakter su volili.

1060
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:54,000
 Jer dođe utakmica,

1061
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:55,000
 trening,

1062
00:44:55,000 --> 00:44:56,000
 ti se ničega ne bojiš,

1063
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:57,000
 ničega se ne plašiš,

1064
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:58,000
 ne povlačiš se.

1065
00:44:58,000 --> 00:44:59,000
 Oni udaraju,

1066
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:00,000
 ti postaviš nogo,

1067
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:01,000
 on padne,

1068
00:45:01,000 --> 00:45:02,000
 pa ti se boji.

1069
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:03,000
 To, to.

1070
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:04,000
 U naše vreme pričam,

1071
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:05,000
 sada je duga priča.

1072
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:06,000
 Da.

1073
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:07,000
 Karakter su volili naš.

1074
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:08,000
 kvalitet je onako,

1075
00:45:08,000 --> 00:45:09,000
 enako,

1076
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,000
 ali karakter nisu smeli.

1077
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:12,000
 Naš kako,

1078
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:13,000
 Portovo se udaralo,

1079
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:14,000
 ali ali tu se postaviš,

1080
00:45:14,000 --> 00:45:15,000
 vidi,

1081
00:45:15,000 --> 00:45:16,000
 udariš me,

1082
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:17,000
 znači ti si gotovo,

1083
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:18,000
 možeš sedam od vas dođe.

1084
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:19,000
 I oni se uplašaju.

1085
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:21,000
 To su se toliko bojali.

1086
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:22,000
 I svuda isto,

1087
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:23,000
 da imamo,

1088
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:24,000
 u Grčkoj,

1089
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:25,000
 u Španiji,

1090
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:26,000
 svuda karakter.

1091
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:27,000
 I onda trener,

1092
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:28,000
 znaš kako je trener vidio.

1093
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:30,000
 Znali su da smo luđi od od njih.

1094
00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:31,000
 Da, vidi,

1095
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:32,000
 viš kako trener vidio,

1096
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:33,000
 sovi mogu vrata.

1097
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:34,000
 Je.

1098
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:35,000
 što je jako bitno.

1099
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:36,000
 Mnogo met kontakt,

1100
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:37,000
 kontakt sport.

1101
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:39,000
 Da se vratim veš malo na reprezentaciju.

1102
00:45:39,000 --> 00:45:41,000
 Kako je tvoje mišljenje?

1103
00:45:41,000 --> 00:45:42,000
 Meni, osobno,

1104
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:43,000
 reprezentacija Slovenije

1105
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:44,000
 čini i jako kvalitetne stvari,

1106
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,000
 konkretne stvari.

1107
00:45:45,000 --> 00:45:47,000
 I sad su prvi u skupini.

1108
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:49,000
 Tvoje mišljenje,

1109
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:51,000
 je li se tu moglo bolje,

1110
00:45:51,000 --> 00:45:52,000
 šta je realnost?

1111
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:54,000
 Misliš ova reprezentacija?

1112
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:55,000
 Da, ova reprezentacija

1113
00:45:55,000 --> 00:45:57,000
 i dok si ti je išao kroz nju.

1114
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:58,000
 Mi kad smo išli,

1115
00:45:58,000 --> 00:46:00,000
 mi smo bili ipak iz one druge baze.

1116
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:01,000
 Iz 24 milijona baze.

1117
00:46:01,000 --> 00:46:03,000
 To je bila puno, da.

1118
